{"tid":2352754,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「三罷」涉大埔路軌擲竹枝 3被告罪成還押候判 1被告罪名不成立但曾被還柙近5個月","createTime":"2021-01-04T08:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T13:10:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"061ca9302f15658ae06f906f534489abce94996a","tid":2352754,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:40:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12604&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=58f7654a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12604</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第三庭 <br />\n#黃國輝裁判官<br />\n#1111大埔 #裁決<br />\n<br />\nD1王(16)<br />\nD5何(22)<br />\nD6郭(27)<br />\nD7呂(20)<br />\n<br />\n早前另外3名被告已認罪（D2D4 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8591&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=78c1fc7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8591</a>)，D3 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8580&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=73a8ca99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8580</a>) ）<br />\n<br />\n【控罪】<br />\n(1)D1-6：意圖危害乘客等的安全而在鐵路上放置物品罪<br />\n（第212章《侵害人身罪條例》第32條；最高刑罰監禁14年）<br />\n(5)D7：管有攻擊性武器或非法用途工具<br />\n（即2萬用刀1錘1鉗2螺絲批）<br />\n(7)D1-6：危害他人安全（控罪(1)的交替控罪）<br />\n（第556章《香港鐵路條例》第30條；最高刑罰罰款$100,000及監禁3年）<br />\n<br />\n❌被告全不認罪❌<br />\n<br />\n裁決：<br />\n‼️法庭宣布D1，D5，D6罪名成立，需要還押。<br />\nD7罪名不成立，當庭釋放。‼️<br />\n（詳情後補）<br />\n<br />\n法庭表示需要押後2星期為各被告索取報告。因為認為拋擲大量竹枝是相當嚴重的案情，最高條例為判處2年，就著d1為其索取更生報告。對於d5，d6，為其索取背景報告再作決定。因為判處監禁是無可避免，三人期間需要還押‼️。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2021年1月18日1430於粉嶺裁判法院判刑。<br />\n（抱歉，審訊和裁決詳情今晚會補回，謝謝～）"},{"pid":"af58222c4c4d01522075fb9583dbc9ddc425c64e","tid":2352754,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"希望攬炒巴可以入嚟睇我呢個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2352628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2352628</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9a4404bf518bf1d52986dd3a2b2596910db438e","tid":2352754,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af58222c4c4d01522075fb9583dbc9ddc425c64e","tid":2352754,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"希望攬炒巴可以入嚟睇我呢個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2352628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2352628</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef2b683cd76997b654e3b7b80daf43b8a4cf589","tid":2352754,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bf3874facff95fe42b9361b981d22ceb8e5100","tid":2352754,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ef2b683cd76997b654e3b7b80daf43b8a4cf589","tid":2352754,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:47:44.000Z","msg":